snippet.title: 【HD】Gotta Protectors
snippet.description:
We are introducing the new game for Nintendo 3DS ...
"Gotta Protectors" !
Gotta Protectors is 8-bit style game for Nintendo 3DS.
A cooperative action, tower defense game.

**web site **
http://www.ancient.co.jp/~game/gotta_protectors/

Coming 7/28/2016 on Nintendo 3DS eShop !

* 8/4/2016 We changed rating level of this game. Really sorry for changing again. 
**changed release date !
*** We are really sorry ,,, deleted old movie and all comments were gone unintentionally .
